Package: ckm
Type: Package
Title: Applying the Cell Key Method (CKM) to protect tabular data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Julien", "Jamme", , "julien.jamme@insee.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(, "Institut National de la Statistique et des Études Économiques", , role = "cph")
  )
Maintainer: Julien Jamme <dg75-dmcsi-confidentialite@insee.fr>
URL: https://github.com/InseeFrLab/ckm
BugReports: https://github.com/InseeFrLab/ckm/issues
Description: 
    The ckm package implements the Cell Key Method (CKM) to protect tabular data and
    provides tools to choose the best parameters to ensure the balance between data 
    utility and privacy protection. The CKM is a method for protecting sensitive data
    in tabular form by applying random keys to cells.
